	(2143,876,'_feedback_email','a:4:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"[Goodbye Picasso] Contact\";s:7:\"message\";s:535:\"Name: shervin\nEmail: ohshervin@gmail.com\nWebsite: http://www.shervinfoto.com\nMessage: Hey There!\r\n\r\ni\'m Shervin - a Brooklyn based music photographer -\r\nwe have some mutual friends so i thought i\'d reach out and say if you ever need new promo/press photos let me know!\r\nmy rates are low and my turn around is fast. here is my work: \r\nwww.ShervinFoto.com\r\n\r\nbest!\r\nshervin\n\nTime: Thursday July 25, 2013 at 5:07 pm\nIP Address: 74.73.105.151\nContact Form URL: http://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/\nSent by an unverified visitor to your site.\";s:7:\"headers\";s:128:\"From: shervin <wordpress@goodbyepicasso.com>\r\nReply-To: shervin <ohshervin@gmail.com>\r\nContent-Type: text/plain; charset=\"UTF-8\"\";}'),
	(2132,875,'_feedback_email','a:4:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"[Goodbye Picasso] Contact\";s:7:\"message\";s:939:\"Name: Askhat Myrzakasym\nEmail: icykeng5@gmail.com\nMessage: Hello, my favorite band Goodbye Picasso! I infinitely admire you. You make great music. I listen to it anywhere, at home and at work. You are very talented. You are SUPER! I apologize for my English. You are the best band in the world. When I listen to your music, I understand that better than you no one else. Really like your album «The Village». I\'m your big fan. I created a Fan Club \"Fan club Goodbye Picasso\". I want to become as great musician like you. I would like to get your autograph with the inscription \"to Askhat.\" Please send me your autograph. Thank you very much. YOU ARE THE BEST!  \r\n\r\nMy Adress:\r\nCountry:KAZAKHSTAN\r\nCity:Zharkent\r\nZIP: 041300\r\nName: Askhat Myrzakasym\r\nStreet: Abdulina 33/5\n\nTime: Wednesday June 19, 2013 at 6:34 am\nIP Address: 178.90.101.190\nContact Form URL: http://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/\nSent by an unverified visitor to your site.\";s:7:\"headers\";s:147:\"From: Askhat Myrzakasym <wordpress@goodbyepicasso.com>\r\nReply-To: Askhat Myrzakasym <icykeng5@gmail.com>\r\nContent-Type: text/plain; charset=\"UTF-8\"\";}'),
