	(2129,875,'_feedback_all_fields','a:4:{s:4:\"Name\";s:17:\"Askhat Myrzakasym\";s:5:\"Email\";s:18:\"icykeng5@gmail.com\";s:7:\"Website\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"Message\";s:714:\"Hello, my favorite band Goodbye Picasso! I infinitely admire you. You make great music. I listen to it anywhere, at home and at work. You are very talented. You are SUPER! I apologize for my English. You are the best band in the world. When I listen to your music, I understand that better than you no one else. Really like your album «The Village». I\'m your big fan. I created a Fan Club \"Fan club Goodbye Picasso\". I want to become as great musician like you. I would like to get your autograph with the inscription \"to Askhat.\" Please send me your autograph. Thank you very much. YOU ARE THE BEST!  \r\n\r\nMy Adress:\r\nCountry:KAZAKHSTAN\r\nCity:Zharkent\r\nZIP: 041300\r\nName: Askhat Myrzakasym\r\nStreet: Abdulina 33/5\";}'),
