	(13786,2248,'_feedback_email','a:2:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"message\";s:1436:\"<b>Name:</b> Shelby Nixon<br /><br /><b>Email:</b> go4designsite@gmail.com<br /><br /><b>Website:</b> http://none<br /><br /><b>Message:</b> Hi I\'m Shelby and I develop beautiful websites for my clients while staying within their budgets.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI specialize in helping companies get the look and feel they want without it costing them an arm and a leg.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMy team and I have an extensive and inexpensive range of digital services that yield a great returns right through to the bottom line. These include app development, e-commerce, responsive mobile sites, SEO, social media and much, much more.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you\'d like to see what we we\'ve done for other companies and learn from their experience with us I would be delighted to share them with you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet me know what time works best so I can share my ideas on what we can do for you and your site.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll the best,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShelby Nixon<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI emailed you today because I wanted to know if you needed any help with your site. If you do not wish to receive my tips on what is working in today\'s online marketing world just let me know by replying to this email with remove in the subject line and I will take your info off my list.<br /><br />Time: February 10, 2016 at 8:44 pm<br />IP Address: 23.80.155.163<br />Contact Form URL: http://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/<br />Sent by an unverified visitor to your site.\";}'),
