	(14515,2497,'_feedback_email','a:2:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"message\";s:1642:\"<!doctype html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<body>\n\n<b>Name:</b> Would you like your business to be on tv?<br /><br /><b>Email:</b> steve@accuratemediasolutions.info<br /><br /><b>Website:</b> http://accuratemediasolutions.info<br /><br /><b>Message:</b> Hi there! <br />\r\n I honestly can\'t think of any business that wouldn\'t want their business in a tv commercial.<br />\r\n However its really expensive and so untargeted! How many sales or customers do you think you will gain if you had a commercial running when they were looking for your business? <br />\r\n My name is Steve and I am looking to work with a few businesses for an online commercial. Instead of being on TV, I want to put your business front and center with a video billboard (commercial) on Google &amp; Youtube in your local area. Not just 1. Not just 5. Not just 10. <br />\r\n But a complete domination of your local market with as many video billboard commercials that it takes to dominate your area. <br />\r\n How many new customers will you get if they search for your service or product and all they see are billboards showcasing you? <br />\r\n I have a few spots open. To see proof of results and what it can do for you please go to http://accuratemediasolutions.info to see some sample results and how we can do the same for you. <br />\r\n Looking forward to hearing from you. <br />\r\n Steve <br />\r\n http://accuratemediasolutions.info<br /><br /><br /><hr />Time: August 3, 2017 at 8:37 am<br />IP Address: 104.144.187.26<br />Contact Form URL: https://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/<br /><p>Sent by an unverified visitor to your site.</p>\n\n</body>\n</html>\";}'),
