	(14179,2380,'_feedback_email','a:2:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"message\";s:1058:\"<b>Name:</b> Tony Long<br /><br />\n<b>Email:</b> tony@tlaudio.net<br /><br />\n<b>Website:</b> http://www.tlaudio.net<br /><br />\n<b>Message:</b> Hello, gentlemen.  I\'m reaching out to you today in the hopes of stealing some of your time tonight after your set to talk about your future recordings.  I am a Music Producer from New York City with a base in Manchester, UK as well, and I\'m digging your tunes, particularly O\'Connor Blues.  If it was distorted and cranked louder, it would sound like The Living End to me, which is one of my all time favorite bands. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI\'ll be in the Rockwood area tonight checking out sets both there and probably Arlene\'s Grocery or Bowery Electric.  As of right now, it looks like I\'m heading over to see you guys.  Lets talk over a beer about what you\'re looking to do in the near future.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nBest,<br />\r\nTL<br /><br />\n\nTime: December 10, 2016 at 5:47 pm<br />\nIP Address: 72.229.213.48<br />\nContact Form URL: https://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/<br />\nSent by an unverified visitor to your site.\";}'),
