	(385,1,'2010-08-13 19:28:34','2010-08-13 19:28:34','Still making improvements/changes/edits/fixes to the site. Trying out a lot of Flash-like things without having to use the monstrosity that is Flash. Things like Web fonts and CSS3 are new and can be tricky, especially on Internet Explorer. <a href=\"http://www.google.com/chrome\" target=\"_blank\">Here is where you should go if you use Internet Exlorer </a>.\r\n\r\nAnyways, pardon our dust for now!','We\'re still in Beta, yo','','publish','open','open','','were-still-in-beta-yo','','','2010-08-13 19:30:20','2010-08-13 19:30:20','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=385',0,'post','',0),
	(386,1,'2010-08-16 18:41:54','2010-08-16 18:41:54','<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/dp/B003V5JOT4?tag=pageturners0c&amp;link_code=as3&amp;creativeASIN=B003V5JOT4&amp;creative=373489&amp;camp=211189\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"The Book of Aylene\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51rgP6WnQ0L._SL500_AA280_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" height=\"280\" /></a>\r\n<blockquote>â€œIf you are looking for something new â€” something truly artistic and enjoyable from a group we should all get to know better â€” be sure to check out Goodbye Picasso\'sÂ <em>The Book of Aylene</em> when it\'s released on August 24. It\'s going to be a hard album to follow upâ€</blockquote>\r\nRead more: <a href=\"http://blogcritics.org/music/article/music-review-goodbye-picasso-the-book/\">Music Review: Goodbye Picasso - The Book of Aylene</a>','The first review is in!','','publish','open','open','','the-first-review-is-in','','','2010-08-16 18:52:55','2010-08-16 18:52:55','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=386',0,'post','',3),
	(387,1,'2010-08-16 19:18:36','2010-08-16 19:18:36','<object classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" width=\"640\" height=\"385\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/Fu7Xn298WWg?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"640\" height=\"385\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/Fu7Xn298WWg?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object>\r\n\r\nChris Dreyer, Scott Taylor, and Dalton Ridenhour perform stripped-down version of \"The Song That Says Goodbye\" in Googie\'s Lounge at The Living Room in New York City.','\"The Song That Says Goodbye\" - (Acoustic) at The Living Room','','publish','open','open','','the-song-that-says-goodbye-acoustic-at-the-living-room','','','2010-08-17 23:25:09','2010-08-17 23:25:09','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=video&p=387',0,'video','',1),
	(388,1,'2010-08-17 19:07:34','2010-08-17 19:07:34','We are playing the new and beautiful Rockwood Music Hall Stage 2 for the first time on August 27, coinciding with the official digital release of THE BOOK OF AYLENE on iTunes, eMusic, and Amazon. We will also be celebrating guitarist Scott Taylor\'s birthday at the gig and after-party! Definitely one not to miss.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/rockwood-poster.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-389\" title=\"Goodbye Picasso @ Rockwood Music Hall Stage 2, August 27\" src=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/rockwood-poster.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"429\" /></a>','August 27 - iTunes album launch party / show at Rockwood Music Hall Stage 2','','publish','open','open','','august-27-itunes-album-launch-party-show-at-rockwood-music-hall-stage-2','','','2010-08-17 19:07:34','2010-08-17 19:07:34','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=388',0,'post','',0),
	(389,1,'2010-08-17 19:05:23','2010-08-17 19:05:23','','Goodbye Picasso @ Rockwood Music Hall Stage 2, August 27','','inherit','open','open','','rockwood-poster','','','2010-08-17 19:05:23','2010-08-17 19:05:23','',388,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/rockwood-poster.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),
	(416,1,'2010-08-28 22:04:16','2010-08-28 22:04:16','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-417\" title=\"Radeberger\" src=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/photo-15.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"604\" height=\"453\" />\r\n\r\nRockwood Music Hall Stage 2 is a great new venue, complete with artist green room and a piano that they lower from the ceiling. Radeberger sponsored the gig and gave us a free case of beer, which we drank in ~20 minutes.\r\n\r\nThanks to everyone that came out to the gig, it was fun!','Radeberger hooked us up','','publish','open','open','','radeberger-hooked-us-up','','','2010-08-28 22:04:16','2010-08-28 22:04:16','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=416',0,'post','',0),
	(391,1,'2010-08-17 23:38:04','2010-08-17 23:38:04','http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPFKbv9G1A8','\"Voices, Villains, Shadows & Ghosts\" - Live at Ars Nova 7.23.10','','publish','open','open','','voices-villains-shadows-ghosts-live-at-ars-nova-7-23-10','','','2010-08-17 23:38:04','2010-08-17 23:38:04','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=video&p=391',0,'video','',0),
	(393,1,'2010-08-24 14:55:03','2010-08-24 14:55:03','THE BOOK OF AYLENE is now available on iTunes! Here is the link: <a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-book-of-aylene/id381329114\" target=\"_blank\">click me</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-book-of-aylene/id381329114\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-394\" title=\"The Book of Aylene\" src=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/boa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" height=\"280\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe tracks may be out of order, go here if they are: <a href=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/album/the-book-of-aylene/\">https://goodbyepicasso.com/album/the-book-of-aylene/</a>','\"The Book of Aylene\" now available on iTunes!','','publish','open','open','','the-book-of-aylene-now-available-on-itunes','','','2010-08-24 14:55:03','2010-08-24 14:55:03','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=393',0,'post','',0),
	(394,1,'2010-08-24 14:54:09','2010-08-24 14:54:09','','The Book of Aylene','','inherit','open','open','','boa','','','2010-08-24 14:54:09','2010-08-24 14:54:09','',393,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/boa.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),
	(420,1,'2010-09-06 05:41:07','2010-09-06 05:41:07','<a href=\"http://www.liveatbestbuy.com/live/goodbye-picasso\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421\" title=\"bestbuy\" src=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/bestbuy.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"199\" height=\"59\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWe will be performing at the Best Buy - Union Square on 9/22 and Best Buy - Chelsea on 10/9, part of Best Buy\'s \"Live @ Best Buy\" series. Should be cool, although interestingly enough: you will not be able to purchase our album at the shows... maybe we can suggest some other albums you might dig while you are there... if you still buy CDs, or maybe we\'ll suggest some funny DVDs, or a Wii game... also they sell Macs at Best Buy - have you made the switch yet !?!\r\n\r\nMore info: <a href=\"http://www.liveatbestbuy.com/live/goodbye-picasso\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.liveatbestbuy.com/live/goodbye-picasso</a>','2 in-store performances in NYC, Live @ Best Buy','','publish','open','open','','live-at-best-buy','','','2010-09-06 22:22:11','2010-09-06 22:22:11','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=420',0,'post','',0),
