	(585,1,'2010-10-28 02:51:19','2010-10-28 02:51:19','Tobacco Road was a cool show, Karen Dreyer PACKED the place for us... so awesome! We took 2 days off in Miami to do some straight chillin, hit up Waxy O\'Connor\'s on Halloween','Tobacco Road - Miami, FL','','publish','open','open','','tobacco-road-miami-fl','','','2010-11-12 02:52:03','2010-11-12 02:52:03','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=gallery&p=585',0,'gallery','',0),
	(453,1,'2010-10-23 23:25:49','2010-10-23 23:25:49','1st gig of the tour, the night was all ours (no openers) - we ate some BBQ at Ed Boudreaux pre-show and then played through a big chunk of our catalog at the show','Emerald Lounge - Asheville, NC','','publish','open','closed','','102310-emerald-lounge-asheville-nc','','','2014-09-08 22:11:01','2014-09-09 02:11:01','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=gallery&#038;p=453',0,'gallery','',0),
