	(824,1,'2011-06-22 14:49:36','2011-06-22 14:49:36','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/24928669?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0\" width=\"650\" height=\"276\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/24928669\">Notes And Measures (2011)</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/jwh\">Jason Wade Hammonds</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p>','Notes and Measures (Official!)','','publish','open','closed','','notes-and-measures','','','2011-06-22 14:51:24','2011-06-22 14:51:24','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=video&#038;p=824',0,'video','',2),
	(845,1,'2012-02-10 22:19:05','2012-02-10 22:19:05','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-855\" title=\"197658_10100933694919743_8109659_n\" src=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/197658_10100933694919743_8109659_n.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\nWe played a live set on the radio at Clemson University in July of \'11 (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wsbf881\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=150983448256977\">WSBF</a>). The DJ, Jordan Young, sent us the tracks. Behold:\r\n\r\n[playlist artists=\"false\" ids=\"846,847,848,849,850,851,852,853,854\"]','Live on WSBF at Clemson University','','publish','open','open','','live-on-wsbf-at-clemson-university','','','2015-10-26 02:05:10','2015-10-26 06:05:10','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=845',0,'post','',0),
	(1702,1,'2014-03-25 18:01:59','2014-03-25 22:01:59','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-855\" title=\"197658_10100933694919743_8109659_n\" src=\"https://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/197658_10100933694919743_8109659_n.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\nWe played a live set on the radio at Clemson University in July of \'11 (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wsbf881\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=150983448256977\">WSBF</a>). The DJ, Jordan Young, sent us the tracks. Behold:\r\n\r\n[playlist ids=\"846,847,848,849,850,851,852,853,854\"]','Live on WSBF at Clemson University','','inherit','open','open','','845-revision-v1','','','2014-03-25 18:01:59','2014-03-25 22:01:59','',845,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/2014/03/25/845-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(827,1,'2011-06-26 04:47:00','2011-06-26 04:47:00','It\'s official = we are going on tour in July! We have a hot slew of dates booked and are making our way down the East Coast and then way over the breadbasket of America, the Midwest. Chris hails from Minnesota, and this will be our first time playing there (Minneapolis). We are also excited for our first show in Chicago which will also be our first show with our stomachs full of Old Style beer.\r\n\r\nHere\'s the schedule - it\'s gonna be hot, come out and hear some new tunes and post-partay with us!\r\n\r\n7.8 World Cafe Live - Philadelphia, PA\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=193356414046436\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=193356414046436</a>\r\n\r\n7.9 Spike Hill - Brooklyn, NY\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=240706685939631\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=240706685939631</a>\r\n\r\n7.17 Deep South Bar - Raleigh, NC\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=221252734573373\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=221252734573373</a>\r\n\r\n7.19 The House 5 Points - Columbia, SC\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=235200669837593\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=235200669837593</a>\r\n\r\n7.20 Speakeasy - Knoxvile, TN\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119638531456116\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119638531456116</a>\r\n\r\n7.21 The Atlanta Room @ Smith\'s Olde Bar - Atlanta, GA\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=213392602033456\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=213392602033456</a>\r\n\r\n7.22 Lindberg\'s - Springfield, MO\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=138651509546792\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=138651509546792</a>\r\n\r\n7.23 Memory Lanes - Minneapolis, MN\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=220991491267472\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=220991491267472</a>\r\n\r\n7.25 The Project Lodge - Madison, WI\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=139977092743427\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=139977092743427</a>\r\n\r\n7.27 Martyr\'s - Chicago, IL\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=248305161853094\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=248305161853094</a>\r\n\r\n7.29 Wilbert\'s - Cleveland, OH\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119771034776143\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119771034776143</a>\r\n\r\n7.30 The Bitter End - New York, NY\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119658581454834\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119658581454834</a>','Summer Tour!','','publish','open','open','','summer-tour','','','2015-10-26 02:06:14','2015-10-26 06:06:14','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=827',0,'post','',0),
	(2198,1,'2015-10-26 02:06:06','2015-10-26 06:06:06','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt\'s official = we are going on tour in July! We have a hot slew of dates booked and are making our way down the East Coast and then way over the breadbasket of America, the Midwest. Chris hails from Minnesota, and this will be our first time playing there (Minneapolis). We are also excited for our first show in Chicago which will also be our first show with our stomachs full of Old Style beer.\r\n\r\nHere\'s the schedule - it\'s gonna be hot, come out and hear some new tunes and post-partay with us!\r\n\r\n7.8 World Cafe Live - Philadelphia, PA\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=193356414046436\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=193356414046436</a>\r\n\r\n7.9 Spike Hill - Brooklyn, NY\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=240706685939631\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=240706685939631</a>\r\n\r\n7.17 Deep South Bar - Raleigh, NC\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=221252734573373\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=221252734573373</a>\r\n\r\n7.19 The House 5 Points - Columbia, SC\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=235200669837593\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=235200669837593</a>\r\n\r\n7.20 Speakeasy - Knoxvile, TN\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119638531456116\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=119638531456116</a>\r\n\r\n7.21 The Atlanta Room @ Smith\'s Olde Bar - Atlanta, GA\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=213392602033456\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=213392602033456</a>\r\n\r\n7.22 Lindberg\'s - Springfield, MO\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=138651509546792\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=138651509546792</a>\r\n\r\n7.23 Memory Lanes - Minneapolis, MN\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=220991491267472\">http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=220991491267472</a>\r\n\r\n7.25 The Project Lodge - Madison, WI\r\n<a href